</P>
<P>
According to the agreement, the British and Irish prime
ministers proposed that both Protestants and Catholics would
form an Ulster cabinet on July 15 and Irish Republican Army
disarmament started "within days."
</P>
<P>
Clinton said it would give a good opportunity to resolve
difficult problems that had caused violent conflicts over
several decades in Northern Ireland.
</P>
<P>
Clinton said the United States supports the efforts made by
both Britain and Ireland in solving the difficult problem and it
will hold all the parties to their commitments. 
</P>
</TEXT>
