the Beijing municipal government.
</P>
<P>
The Japanese company has given a great deal of care and
attention to China's environmental conditions and began the
activity last year.
</P>
<P>
It has promised to provide three million yuan (360,000 U.S.
dollars) in funds to plant 390,000 trees in the area for three
years and has organized staff members to take part in the activity.
Some 1,400 company members participated in the planting last year.
</P>
