PYONGYANG -- Generals of the Democratic People 's Republic of
Korea (DPRK) and the U.S.-led United Nations Command (UNC)
remained wide apart after meeting for the third time over the
recent inter-Korean naval clash, press reports said Saturday. (
DPRK-US-Talks)
