Sacramento Kings center Vlade Divac finished with eight, after
shooting 1-for-6 from the field in 26 minutes on the court.
</P>
<P>
In the Spain-France match, forward Alberto Herreros scored 29
points for Spain as they entered the final for the first time
since 1983.
</P>
<P>
Jim Bilba had 11 points for France and Antoine Rigaudeau and
Thierry Gadou added 10 apiece.
</P>
<P>
France will now play Yugoslavia for the bronze medal. 
