<HEADLINE> Nigeria Midfielder Oliseh Joins Juventus </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria midfielder Sunday Oliseh
joined Juventus on a five-year contract, the club announced Friday.
</P>
<P>
